frames.caption: Three guinea pigs wearing sunglasses stand confidently in front of a grand architectural structure, resembling the Sagrada Familia. The bright blue sky and detailed facade create a whimsical and humorous scene.

frames.caption: Three guinea pigs wearing sunglasses and bow ties pose confidently in front of the iconic Sagrada Familia. frames.description: The scene is set in front of the Sagrada Familia in Barcelona, where three anthropomorphic guinea pigs are dressed in stylish sunglasses and bow ties. They stand proudly, creating a humorous and surreal juxtaposition with the grand architecture behind them.
